· Crew: 12 persons.
· Mission Duration: 26 months (including 8-month transit).
· Includes Minimum Viable Habitation (MVH) suite for transit and contingency.
· All masses in metric tons (t).

C.2 Detailed Mass Breakdown

Table C.1: Habitation Starship Mass Budget

Subsystem Dry Mass (t) Consumables Mass (t) Total Mass (t) Notes
STRUCTURE & SHELL 85.0 0.0 85.0 Pressure hull, primary floors, exoskeleton attachment points.
LIFE SUPPORT (ECLSS) 8.5 12.0 20.5 Atmospheric revitalization, water recycling, temperature/humidity control. Includes 90-day buffer.
RADIATION SHIELDING 2.0 25.0 27.0 Fixed polyethylene panels + "Water Wall" reservoir (circulated drinking water).
CREW ACCOMMODATIONS 6.0 1.5 7.5 Private quarters (12x), galley, wardroom, hygiene facilities, furnishings.
